Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill allows you to bring ARWA into your home, work, phone, or any other place you have an Alexa Skills enabled device. Initially, this skill will keep you up to date with training initiatives, but soon there will be many other features built to help streamline your work in Alabama's Water and Wastewater Fields.
